meta_title: 3M Black Weatherstrip Adhesive for Vintage MOPAR Cars & Trucks
meta_description: Secure your weatherstripping with 3M Black Weatherstrip Adhesive. Ideal for MOPAR vehicles from 1928-1962. Long-lasting and durable.
product_description:
Revitalize your vintage MOPAR vehicle's weatherstripping with our 3M Brand Black Weatherstrip Adhesive. Perfect for a wide array of MOPAR cars and trucks spanning from 1928 to 1962, this adhesive ensures a strong, durable bond for your weatherstripping, safeguarding your vehicle's interior against the elements and noise pollution.

  • Compatibility: Specially designed for MOPAR vehicles, this weatherstrip adhesive fits models from 1928 to 1962, including both cars and trucks.
  • 3M Quality: Leveraging the reliability and strength of 3M products, this black weatherstrip adhesive guarantees a secure and lasting seal.
  • Application: Ideal for both professional restorers and DIY enthusiasts, our adhesive allows for an easy and clean application process, ensuring your vehicle's weatherstripping remains firmly in place.
  • Versatility: Whether you're restoring a classic car or maintaining a vintage truck, this adhesive meets a wide range of weatherstripping needs, from doors to windows and trunks.

Bring back the original look and feel of your vintage MOPAR vehicle while providing it with the protection it deserves. 3M Brand Black Weatherstrip Adhesive is your go-to solution for weatherstripping applications, ensuring a perfect fit and finish for your classic ride.

meta_description: Shop high-quality reproduction Molded Cowl Vent Gaskets for 1936-1938 Chrysler, DeSoto, Dodge & Plymouth. Perfect fit & durability.
product_description:
Revive the authenticity and functionality of your vintage Mopar vehicle with our Molded Cowl Vent Gasket, a high-quality reproduction of the original Mopar number 742408. Designed with precision to ensure a perfect fit, this molded cowl rubber gasket is the perfect solution to replace your worn or damaged seals, ensuring your engine is protected from water and debris.

  • Features: Exquisitely molded rubber gasket, replicating the original design to ensure a perfect seal and fit.
  • Compatibility: Fits a wide range of Mopar cars from 1936 to 1938, including Chrysler Airstream Deluxe Series C-8, Airstream Series C-7, Custom, Imperial and Royal; DeSoto S-3 and S-5; Dodge Deluxe and Cars D-5, D-6 & D-7; and Plymouth P3, P4, P5, and P6.
  • Exclusions: Please note, this gasket does not fit Airflow models.

Invest in the best for your cherished classic. This Molded Cowl Vent Gasket not only restores the original look and feel of your vintage vehicle but also offers enhanced protection and longevity. Perfect for enthusiasts and restorers alike, it's an essential component for maintaining the integrity of your vehicle's engine bay against the elements.

meta_title: Vintage V8 Main Bearing Set for Dodge, Chrysler & More
meta_description: Premium main bearing set for 1959-73 383, 413, 440, & 426 Wedge V8 engines. Perfect fit for classic Dodge, Chrysler & Plymouth models.
product_description:
Introducing the ultimate solution for restoring the heart of your classic V8 engine - our Main Bearing Set, meticulously designed to fit an extensive range of vintage Dodge, Chrysler, DeSoto, and Plymouth vehicles. This premium-quality bearing set is compatible with 1959-60 383 cui V8, 1959-73 413 cui V8, 1966-73 440 cui V8, and 1963-65 426 Wedge V8 engines, ensuring your classic car regains its original power and smooth performance. It's important to note that this set does not fit the 426 HEMI engines.

Whether you're reviving a 1959 Chrysler Imperial, a muscle-bound 1970 Dodge Challenger, or any of the timeless models in between, this main bearing set guarantees a precise fit and unmatched reliability. Each piece is crafted with the utmost attention to detail, ensuring your classic car's engine runs as smoothly as the day it left the showroom.

Fitment includes a vast array of models from 1959 to 1973, covering icons like the Chrysler 300, Dodge Coronet, Plymouth Fury, and many more, making it a must-have for enthusiasts and restorers dedicated to preserving the legacy of these magnificent machines.

Restore your engine's glory with this essential main bearing set, and let your vintage car roar back to life with the strength and stamina of its youth. Perfect for restorations and rebuilds, ensure your classic stays true to its roots with parts designed for the purist.
